te | Source | Notes | In Tokens | Out Tokens |\\n|------|--------|-------|-----------|------------|\\n');\n_fs.appendFileSync(mdPath, mdLine);\nslog(vaultPath, 'Write-Log', 'info', 'Processing log updated', batchId);\nreturn { json: data };\n"
